;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p>Verst Carbon\u2019s digital Monitoring, Reporting, and Verification (dMRV) platform revolutionizes the way clean cooking initiatives are monitored and verified. By leveraging advanced IoT technology, the platform provides real-time data collection, secure cloud-based data management, and automated reporting, ensuring transparency and accuracy in impact assessments.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Key Features<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>IoT-Enabled Data Collection<\/strong>: Custom IoT devices integrated with cookstoves capture real-time usage and performance data. These devices provide a continuous stream of accurate information, allowing for precise monitoring of project impact.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Secure Data Transmission<\/strong>: The platform employs robust encryption methods to ensure data integrity and confidentiality during transmission. This guarantees that sensitive data remains protected against unauthorized access and tampering.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Cloud-Based Data Management<\/strong>: A scalable and secure cloud infrastructure is used for storing, managing, and analyzing collected data. This ensures data is easily accessible for stakeholders while maintaining high levels of security and reliability.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Automated Reporting<\/strong>: The platform automates the generation of comprehensive reports, streamlining the verification process. Automated reporting reduces the administrative burden and enhances the efficiency and accuracy of the monitoring process.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Global Standards Compliance<\/strong> Verst Carbon\u2019s dMRV platform aligns with the Metered Energy Cooking Devices (MECD) methodology, which sets the standard for credible environmental claims in clean cooking projects. By adhering to these global standards, the platform ensures that the data collected and reported is reliable and internationally recognized.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Community Impact<\/strong> The dMRV platform empowers local communities by providing valuable insights into the usage and effectiveness of clean cooking solutions. Through a user-friendly mobile application, users can access real-time data and engage with the project, fostering a sense of ownership and involvement.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-591a636d elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"591a636d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:600}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.17.0 - 08-11-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1128\" height=\"191\" src=\"https:\/\/verst.earth\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/LinkedIn-Banner.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-2105\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/verst.earth\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/LinkedIn-Banner.png 1128w, https:\/\/verst.earth\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/LinkedIn-Banner-300x51.png 300w, https:\/\/verst.earth\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/0